sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as Body-Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM/SGLang/Triton)

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request Processing (with BBR)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / API Key
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc: RequestHeaders + RequestBody<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS (self-signed)
    BBR->>BBR: Parse JSON body<br/>Extract model name
    BBR->>BBR: Lookup adapter→base model<br/>(from ConfigMap cache)
    BBR-->>Gateway: ext-proc response:<br/>Inject X-Gateway-Model-Name header
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc: RequestHeaders + RequestBody<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS (self-signed)

    Note over EPP: Scheduling Pipeline
    EPP->>EPP: 1. Filter endpoints<br/>(prefix cache affinity, SLO headroom)
    EPP->>EPP: 2. Score endpoints<br/>(KV cache util, queue depth,<br/>LoRA affinity, predicted latency)
    EPP->>EPP: 3. Pick best endpoint<br/>(max score / weighted random)

    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc response:<br/>Set target endpoint address<br/>+ port in headers
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward request to<br/>selected endpoint<br/>HTTP/gRPC
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response<br/>(streaming or unary)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response<br/>(SSE stream or JSON)

    Note over EPP,ModelServer: Flow 2: Continuous Metrics Scraping

    loop Every 50ms (configurable)
        EPP->>ModelServer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (InsecureSkipVerify)
        ModelServer-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics:<br/>KV cache util, queue depth,<br/>running requests, LoRA info
        EPP->>EPP: Update in-memory datastore<br/>with endpoint metrics
    end

    Note over BBR,K8sAPI: Flow 3: CRD & ConfigMap Watches

    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Watch notifications:<br/>InferencePool, InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite, Pods
    EPP->>EPP: Reconcile datastore:<br/>update endpoints, models,<br/>priorities, SLOs

    K8sAPI-->>BBR: Watch notifications:<br/>ConfigMaps (bbr-managed=true)
    BBR->>BBR: Update adapter→base model<br/>mapping cache
